description:
A brand-new Captain America adventure begins! Cap is plagued by nightmares where he loses his strength and his body withers to its original form, before he was given the super-soldier formula! Now, those dreams are coming true… and at the worst possible time!

Also, Thor, God of Thunder, defends the Eternal Realm from any and all threats!

Plus, Iron Man is down, and War Machine battles the Melter, Whirlwind and the Living Laser alone!

Not only that, but we have an awesome competition in which you can win Ultimate Iron Man Bundles, consisting of Iron Man 3 DVDs, Iron Man Arc FX Gauntlet AND Iron Man Mission Mask!

Story and art by Ed Brubaker, Alan Davis, Matt Fraction, Barry Kitson, and Salvador Larroca!

Includes material reprinted from Captain America Vol.6 #6, Invincible Iron Man #515 and Mighty Thor Vol.4 #12.1! 76 pages!
